entry.string: SELECT p.id, p.name, p.description, p.product_number, p.manufactured, p.colors, p.categories, p.stock, p.safety_stock_level, p.standard_cost, p.list_price, p.size, p.size_unit_measure_code, p.weight, p.weight_unit_measure_code, p.days_to_manufacture, p.images, p.modified_date, p.created_date FROM product p LIMIT 10

SELECT p.id, p.name, p.description, p.product_number, p.manufactured, p.colors, p.categories, p.stock, p.safety_stock_level, p.standard_cost, p.list_price, p.size, p.size_unit_measure_code, p.weight, p.weight_unit_measure_code, p.days_to_manufacture, p.images, p.modified_date, p.created_date FROM product p WHERE p.id = #[flowVars.id]
